==English==

===Etymology===
{{L.}} [[metrum]] or {{Gr.}} (metron), ''[[measure]]''

===Suffix===
'''-meter'''

# Used to form the names of [[measuring]] [[device]]s - e.g. [[barometer]]
# Used to form the names of [[line]]s of [[feet]] in [[prosody]] - e.g. [[hexameter]]
#{{US}} Used to form the names of [[unit of measure|units of measure]] - e.g. [[centimeter]]

